      "writtenOn": "2019-04-10T01:17:16Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e Wait why will it be happening? You mean if a new VM is brought online but the index isn\u0027t updated so the query incorrectly returns nothing for awhile? \n\nYes.\n\n\u003e I think that\u0027s fine because it should have the same behavior as the Machine Provider agent, it will fail and chromebuild-startup.py will relaunch it until it doesn\u0027t fail.\n\nOk.",
      "parentUuid": "296afd41_9ddcc0aa",
      "range": {
